From 416fa9e2dc6f5d4b60a8b36514582cdd40e56542 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Fri, 20 Mar 2026 18:30:23 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Audit fixes: security, data safety, and UI robustness
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

JSON repair (OpenRouterClient):
- Rewrite repairMalformedJson with single-pass string-context-aware
  trailing comma removal — no longer corrupts JSON string values
  containing ",}" or ",]" patterns (e.g. file paths, CLI commands)
- Add MAX_REPAIRABLE_JSON_LENGTH (100KB) guard against resource exhaustion
- Cap bracket-closing depth to 10 to limit synthesized structure
- Remove dead `lastNonWs` variable, eliminate regex recompilation

Retry safety (VesperAgent):
- retryLastMessage now only strips the final failed turn, preserving
  earlier successful tool exchanges to avoid re-triggering side-effecting
  Flipper commands (SubGHz transmit, BadUSB, file writes, etc.)

Database (VesperDatabase):
- Add proper Migration(1,2) with ALTER TABLE instead of relying solely
  on fallbackToDestructiveMigration — preserves existing user data
  (audit logs + chat history) on app upgrade
- Scope destructive fallback to fallbackToDestructiveMigrationFrom(1)

Image persistence (VesperAgent):
- Cap persisted image base64 to ~300KB per image to stay within
  Android's 2MB CursorWindow limit, preventing crashes on session restore

UI (ChatScreen + ChatViewModel):
- Add retryInFlight double-tap guard matching approvalDecisionInFlight
- Replace raw Snackbar with SnackbarHost-managed snackbar (dismissible,
  timed, no overlap with input bar)
- Add key = { it.id } to LazyColumn items for correct recomposition
- Use index comparison instead of structural equality for isLastMessage
- Show retry on any last message role, not just ASSISTANT

